    </statement>
    <solution>
        <p>
            <ol>
                <li>
                    <p>
                        To aid in our analysis, we set up a short table of values to give us a frame of
                        reference.
                    </p>
                    <sidebyside>
                    <tabular halign="center" valign="top" left="medium" right="medium" top="medium" bottom="medium"> 
                        <col width="100%"/>
                        <row header="yes" >
