                    </sidebyside>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>To get the graph of <m>y = 3^{x + 1}</m>, we start with the graph of <m>y = 3^{x}</m>, and shift 1 unit to the left.</p>
                    <sidebyside>
                        <image>
